  "No, the additional revenue does not cover the marketing cost": "",
  "CM per session = $60 - $15 = $45. Additional CM from 50 sessions = 50 x $45 = $2,250. Additional cost = $1,500. Net gain = $2,250 - $1,500 = $750. The marketing investment is profitable.": ""
